item.title: Sean Penn: Charlize Theron Would Be My "First Marriage"
item.description: Third time’s a… first? Though married and divorced twice before, Sean Penn told Esquire UK in its March 2015 cover story that he’d consider his future marriage to fiancee Charlize Theron to be his first. “I’ve had relationships that were not with famous people, or people aspiring to be famous,” the two-time Oscar winner reflected of his 35-plus years in Hollywood. “And in some cases they went more poorly! But as it turned out, yes, the two marriages I had were with high-profile people, in their own ways.
